xmlcomponents.autoparse.annotation
Annotation Type XmlProperty

@Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface XmlProperty

This annotation is used to tell the AutoParser which fields it should parse, and what names to expect.

jjnguy
